    • Method Detail

      • submit

        <V> Queuture<V> submit(Informable<QueutureBox<V>> informable)
        Submit a new computation to be asynchronously executed. As the computation is executed, results will become available on a first-come first-serve basis in the returned Queuture.
        Parameters:
        informable - The computation to asynchronously execute.
        Returns:
        A Queuture representing the multiple results of the computation.
        Throws:
        RejectedExecutionException - If the computation cannot be scheduled for execution.
        NullPointerException - If the computation is null.
